1.title: Sousou & Betty Soo - Made of Music
1.plot: Two songwriters get half a day to create one song. From Seed To Song is a web-based series where artists from around the globe meet for intense songwriting sessions. In every episode, we will follow a new pairing. From the planting of ideas and making it all grow to the song being performed. In this episode, you'll meet Sousou Cissoko and Betty Soo while they're writing the song Made of Music.
